Doc: The specification of the Settlement Periods in which the electricity will be delivered for a "shaped" trade i.e. where different Settlement Period ranges will apply to different periods of the trade.

Source.Contents:
/#
   The specification of the Settlement Periods in which the electricity will be delivered for a "shaped" trade i.e. where different Settlement Period ranges will apply to different periods of the trade.
 #/
record FpML5.confirmation.SettlementPeriodsSchedule {
  # The range of Settlement Periods per Calculation Period. There must be a range of Settlement Periods specified for each Calculation Period, regardless of whether the range of Settlement Periods changes or stays the same between periods.
  settlementPeriodsStep : FpML5.confirmation.SettlementPeriodsStep

  # A pointer style reference to the Delivery Periods defined elsewhere.
  deliveryPeriodsReference : FpML5.confirmation.CalculationPeriodsReference

  # A pointer style reference to the Calculation Periods Schedule defined elsewhere.
  deliveryPeriodsScheduleReference : FpML5.confirmation.CalculationPeriodsScheduleReference

}

settlementPeriodsStep.Doc: The range of Settlement Periods per Calculation Period. There must be a range of Settlement Periods specified for each Calculation Period, regardless of whether the range of Settlement Periods changes or stays the same between periods.
settlementPeriodsStep.Name: settlementPeriodsStep

deliveryPeriodsReference.Doc: A pointer style reference to the Delivery Periods defined elsewhere.
deliveryPeriodsReference.Name: deliveryPeriodsReference

deliveryPeriodsScheduleReference.Name: deliveryPeriodsScheduleReference
